name: Services that exposes the vendor to any potential Adverse Event reporting situations, such as Market Research and Patient Support Program (MAP), Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Non-MAP/Other Data Related, Non-Interventional Study (NIS).
Commercial activities involving competitive intelligence, public relations, or primary market research.
Sending or receiving personally identifiable information (PII) (e.g. protected health information (PHI), or information regarding individual employee(s) information, vendor(s) or consultant(s).

Services, payment/transfer of value(s), directly or indirectly, with any Healthcare Provider, including physicians, nurses, pharmacists, hospitals or other healthcare organizations, and patients or their advocates, whether direct or indirect, through a vendor or otherwise (except for US Commercial: M&CS preferred logistics vendors).

Services or activities relating to or involving (a) hazardous waste or materials; (b) ecological, environmental, toxicological or human health assessments or studies; or (c) other environmental, health & safety (EHS) related matters
